        </item>
        <item>
            <title>FlightRadar24 直擊國泰航班盤旋 2 小時，黃雨下兩次着陸失敗有人已寫好遺書</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/02/flightradar-24-cathay-shanghai-to-hk-plane/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=flightradar-24-cathay-shanghai-to-hk-plane</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/02/flightradar-24-cathay-shanghai-to-hk-plane/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 11:30:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅遊]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Flightradar24]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1232900</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日香港天氣非常不穩定，日前（4 月 30 日）天文台一度發出黃色暴雨警告，部分到港航班受影響無法在港降落。國泰航空一班由上海飛抵香港的 CX341 航班受大雨影響，曾 2 次試圖着陸失敗，Flightradar24 紀錄了整個驚險的旅程，顯示 CX341 最終在香港上空盤旋近 2 小時後轉飛轉降深圳加油，其後再重新飛返香港。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232901" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/438137553_8113645075-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/438137553_8113645075-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/438137553_8113645075.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p>據《Channel C》引述航班乘客指，飛機內情況非常混亂，期間有多個乘客嘔吐，部分乘客因飛機多次急速爬升引發缺氧反應。有自稱乘搭涉事航班的網民表示當時自己已寫好遺書。</p><p>由 Flightradar24 的路線可見，這架飛機二度嘗試降落未果，於是在香港空域盤旋逾 2 小時，惟一直無法把握降落時機，最終轉飛往中國深圳寶安國際機場降落並加油，其後再飛香港方成功降落。由下圖可見，飛機在 5 分鐘內由 750 呎急速爬升至 6,175 呎。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232909" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502170742-686x580.jpg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502170742-686x580.jpg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502170742.jpg 1064w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232908" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502170807-631x580.jpg" alt="" width="631" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502170807-631x580.jpg 631w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502170807.jpg 980w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 631px" /></p><div></div><div><p>Flightradar24 是瑞典一間提供即時飛行器飛行狀況的互聯網服務商，用户可以在其網站讀取航班飛行軌跡、出發地、目的地預計到達時間、飛行高度及速度等等。</p></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://channelchk.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E9%A3%9B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%81%87%E9%9B%B7%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%A8%E8%A9%A6%E9%99%8D%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E6%80%A5%E5%8D%87%E5%8D%83%E7%B1%B3-%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD%E7%9B%A4%E6%97%8B2%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E5%B0%96%E5%8F%AB%E5%98%94%E5%90%90%E7%B6%93%E6%AD%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E6%99%82%E5%88%BB#google_vignette">Channel C</a>、<a href="https://www.flightradar24.com/data/flights/cx341#34fefc6a">Flightradar24</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/02/flightradar-24-cathay-shanghai-to-hk-plane/life-tech/travel/">FlightRadar24 直擊國泰航班盤旋 2 小時，黃雨下兩次着陸失敗有人已寫好遺書</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
