        <item>
            <title>Netflix 新訂閲無法再選 Basic 　香港暫未受影響</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/02/netflix-is-setting-new-standards-the-end-of-the-basic-subscription-is-approaching/movie-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=netflix-is-setting-new-standards-the-end-of-the-basic-subscription-is-approaching</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/02/netflix-is-setting-new-standards-the-end-of-the-basic-subscription-is-approaching/movie-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:45:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影視娛樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Netflix]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1232864</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前串流平台巨頭 Netflix 公佈 2024 年首季業績，儘管訂閲人數、營收或獲利均超出預期（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/19/netflix-17/movie-2/">相關報道</a>），但近日外國有網民就表示 Netflix 取消了最便宜無廣告的「Basic 」基本方案，要求他在訂閲期結束後改為選擇更貴的方案。</p><p>Reddit 用户 <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/RKDreddit/">@RKDreddit</a> 日前分享了一封來自 Netflix 的電郵，要求他在今期訂閲結束後升級更貴的方案，倘若訂閲期結束後一個月內 @RKDreddit 沒有選擇新方案，Netflix 會終止其會員。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232866" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/mildlyinfuriating/comments/1cgde33/netflix_is_discontinuing_its_most_popular_and/">RKDreddit@Reddit</a></p><p>@RDKreddit 另外亦上傳了一張螢幕截圖，可見 Netflix 已經取消最便宜無廣告的「Basic」方案，如果用户不想看廣告，就要升級至 16.49 美元（約港幣 129 元）的「Standard」方案，或者是選擇 5.99 美元（約港幣 47 元）的有廣告「Standard with ads」方案。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232867" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/netflixisdiscontinui-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/mildlyinfuriating/comments/1cgde33/netflix_is_discontinuing_its_most_popular_and/">RKDreddit@Reddit</a></p><p>截止今日（5 月 2 日）下午 1 時，香港 Netflix 仍然提供基本方案。值得留意的是，香港 Netflix 上月亦調整了訂閲費用：</p><p>高級 4K+HDR $93→$108（加幅：16%）</p><p>標準 1080p $78→$88（加幅：12.8%）</p><p>基本 720p $63→$73（加幅：15.9%）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232868" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502131022-408x580.jpg" alt="" width="408" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502131022-408x580.jpg 408w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240502131022.jpg 633w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 408px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://help.netflix.com/zh-tw/node/24926">Netflix</a></p><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/765/528.htm">IT Home</a>、<a href="https://www.breakinglatest.news/technology/netflix-is-setting-new-standards-the-end-of-the-basic-subscription-is-approaching/">Breaking Latest News</a>、<a href="https://help.netflix.com/zh-tw/node/24926">Netflix</a><br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/19/netflix-17/movie-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Netflix 打擊共享密碼取得成功，首季訂閲人數激增超預期</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/08/netflix-16/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Netflix 香港加價 4K 計劃加 $15 變每月 $108</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/05/disney-will-crack-down-on-password-sharing-in-june/movie-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Disney+ 6 月起嚴打共用帳户    CEO：Netflix 是串流媒體領域的標準</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/02/netflix-is-setting-new-standards-the-end-of-the-basic-subscription-is-approaching/movie-2/">Netflix 新訂閲無法再選 Basic 　香港暫未受影響</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
